    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; DT, 9 and 10 Engine Service Manual - Variable Geometry Turbocharger
        (VGT) - Installation
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
            <title>VGT Assembly and Oil Drain Tube</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install a new O-ring on each end of the turbocharger oil drain tube and lubricate with
                    clean engine oil.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <specpara>
                <caution>
                    <para>To prevent engine damage, use care to not damage oil drain tube O-rings.</para>
                </caution>
            </specpara>
            <figure id="f3350004" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figK15/K15011.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>VGT assembly rear view</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil supply port</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">VGT mounting stud</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil drain port</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install one end of the oil drain tube into the VGT oil drain port.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Place a new turbocharger mounting gasket over VGT mounting studs.</para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f3350004127" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figk15/K15003.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>VGT mounting</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M10 Spiralock&#174; nut (4)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger mounting gasket</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">VGT mounting stud</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <specpara>
                <warning>
                    <para>To prevent personal injury or death, support turbocharger assembly during removal and
                        installation.
                    </para>
                </warning>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lift VGT assembly onto engine and insert VGT mounting studs into the exhaust manifold
                    and install two new M10 Spiralock&#174; nuts on the VGT mounting studs.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Pre-lube the VGT assembly by adding oil to the oil supply port while rotating the
                    turbine shaft. Continue to add oil until oil comes out the oil drain tube.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the oil drain tube into the crankcase.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install two new M10 Spiralock&#174; nuts on the exhaust manifold studs.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Verify the oil drain tube is seated in the crankcase oil drain port.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten four M10 nuts to
                    <hotlnk document="eges3351_118.xml" xrefid="t335000402">special torque</hotlnk>
                    <xref refid="t335000402"/>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f3350004128" figsize="pg-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figk15/K15002.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="312px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Turbocharger oil drain tube, bracket, and bolt</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 16 bolt</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Tube bracket (oil drain)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger oil drain tube</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Align oil drain tube then install tube bracket and M8 x 16 bolt.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten M8 x 16 bolt to
                    <hotlnk document="eges3351_SAPPB01.xml" xrefid="sAppB01">standard torque</hotlnk>
                    <xref refid="sAppB01"/>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install turbocharger air intake duct on the VGT and crankcase breather assemblies.
                    Tighten worm gear clamps on turbocharger air intake duct and breather tube.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
